data.description:
Welcome to this charming two-story home situated on a large corner lot, offering both space and serenity. Boasting four generously-sized bedrooms and two and a half baths, this residence is designed to accommodate modern living with ease and comfort.

As you step inside, you're greeted by an abundance of natural light flooding through the windows, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout the home. The spacious layout provides ample room for both relaxation and entertainment, with a seamless flow from room to room.

The main level features a well-appointed kitchen, perfect for culinary enthusiasts, complete with modern appliances and plenty of counter space. Adjacent to the kitchen is a cozy dining area, ideal for enjoying family meals or hosting guests.

Upstairs, you'll find the tranquil sleeping quarters, including the master suite with its own private bath, offering a peaceful retreat at the end of the day. Three additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family members or guests, each offering comfort and privacy.

Outside, the expansive corner lot offers endless possibilities for outdoor enjoyment, whether it's gardening, hosting summer barbecues, or simply basking in the sunshine. With its manicured landscaping and well-maintained exterior, this home exudes curb appeal and pride of ownership.

Located in a desirable neighborhood, close to amenities and attractions, this home combines the best of suburban living with the comforts of home. Don't miss your chance to make this immaculate residence your own – schedule a showing today and experience all it has to offer!
